{"tid":1524914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 水砲車可以咁解決","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T19:39:29.000Z","uid":194998,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81e8b018c23cbf4c4c92dd8bce01cc335175bcfe","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"唔知今日大家有冇跑過千人一里發夢大賽跑呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多未係企得好前嘅巴絲未必知道最前線發生咩事。今日其實就係水砲車沿住大直路射下停下，加埋催淚彈cover，令到大家要不斷跑。以下係個人對警犬水砲車tactics嘅分析。<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先有警犬發射催淚彈，嚇走最前排嘅勇武。等待警犬清理roadblock，幫水砲車開路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 然後水砲車不斷停下射下，大直路下無限推進，逼走手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0cKc7z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0cKc7z.png&h=938500cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢呢個tactics好似好屈機，水砲車可以做移動砲台攻擊群眾，警犬又會守起隔離。勇武又行唔得前，魔法師又未必到casting area，好似冇得打咁，但其實都有得counter。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢今日個南北推進咁成功，係因為只要清理咗第一排roadblock，水砲車就可以長驅直入，邊行邊射唔畀你抖，仲可以喺短時間內推進成公里。所以小弟推薦以下方法:<br />\n<br />\nRoadblock要喺後面個個街口set，但係唔需要多，只要一兩個三角形就ok，咁樣一嚟可以擋到水砲車一陣，比手足抖抖氣，二嚟又唔會阻住手足走。每個街口set就可以達到defense in layers嘅效果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJb3tLG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJb3tLG.png&h=4a534e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充: 呢個方法唔係真係可以抵擋水砲車，但至少唔使再千人賽跑，俾人追住嚟砌，亦唔會再好似今日咁一咁畀人推進成公里遠，有多啲空間慢慢打。呢個方法係將水砲車嘅功能降到最細，令警方主力都係要用返催淚彈同衝刺推進，還原基本步。而啲roadblock點樣分配交返畀前線決定，但我建議後面至少留一至兩個三角形。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n利申:又攰又眼瞓，不過照出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b0d48f50f49cbc518d975e9b87b547094427f9","tid":1524914,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:00.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=7df3e988\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=14f3bc24\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=e3f351e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"da8be5f32899f4ed9ee8ee009ee85f8eaece5e52","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"815b27102e5923a635007d3efcb8cc751de8e9ec","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"623f2e91cbd82621d85b43850e4485da6089ea63","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8fe0b9e7fe25c86ae0d1bcc75f43aa3312770193","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fe1d4be0b4cdf8bf95249fcf9bea3fc41d5c61de","tid":1524914,"uid":194998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"自