14,"uid":25290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:53:10.000Z","msg":"同意，可以阻礙前進。<br />\n<br />\n要毀滅，可以用無人飛行魔法。"},{"pid":"7202d37277a2c8201edc54bd130b1422d462ecf2","tid":1524914,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"樓主講得無錯，補充一點，我地應該揀個好既戰場，避開大直路呢種方便水炮車既地形"},{"pid":"f2d55d66be8efdfd58745980435baaf2486029b6","tid":1524914,"uid":29014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"妖 我都有係前線提過 但硬係有手足要係障礙物前面企係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂 我地本身就諗住係路邊拎d大巴士路牌打橫放路中心 等架車得慢d<br />\n點知你地硬係唔肯走 我地又唔想到你地要向後跑時kick到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申 不割𥱊 但有待改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7f5e289ff6bef6fba1c2984eda3eac6d5c8424","tid":1524914,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"164f0422ec7dc755c8f7c711f04ce89576895c36","tid":1524914,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:39:29.000Z","msg":"唔好再玩陣地啦 諗過第二個方式 玩左成個月 次次都係等比人清"}]}